\right)$ and $B=\left( \begin{array}{rrr}
4 & 1 & 0 \\ 
-4 & -2 & 4 \\ 
0 & 3 & 1 \end{array}
\right)$.

Find $\mathrm{det} \left(X\right)$ if  $A \cdot X\cdot B -B^2=0$.

